<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>网络协议 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/</link><description>网络协议 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>HTTP演进</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/http%E6%BC%94%E8%BF%9B/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/http%E6%BC%94%E8%BF%9B/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="http演进">HTTP演进</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：HTTP从1.0到3.0的演进主线是&quot;减少连接数→复用连接→消除队头阻塞→降低握手延迟&quot;，每次升级都在解决前一代的瓶颈，但协议复杂度也相应增加。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="http从10到30围绕连接效率队头阻塞握手延迟三个核心问题逐步优化">HTTP从1.0到3.0围绕连接效率、队头阻塞、握手延迟三个核心问题逐步优化</h2>
<h3 id="http10无状态的请求-响应协议">HTTP/1.0：无状态的请求-响应协议</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">每次请求新建TCP连接：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">客户端                  服务端
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  TCP握手 (SYN-SYN/ACK-ACK)  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  | &lt;-------------------------&gt; |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |      GET /page1.html        |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  ------------------------&gt;  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |      200 OK + 数据           |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  &lt;------------------------  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |      TCP挥手 (FIN-ACK...)   |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  | &lt;-------------------------&gt; |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  [下一个请求重复以上全过程]</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>核心问题</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>每个请求独立TCP连接，三次握手开销大</li>
<li>无法复用连接，浏览器同时只能发少量请求（6-8个域名并发）</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="http11持久连接与管道化">HTTP/1.1：持久连接与管道化</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>特性</th>
          <th>说明</th>
          <th>解决的问题</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>持久连接（Keep-Alive）</td>
          <td>复用TCP连接发送多个请求</td>
          <td>减少握手开销</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>管道化（Pipelining）</td>
          <td>连续发送多个请求不等待响应</td>
          <td>提高吞吐量</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>分块传输（Chunked）</td>
          <td>服务端分块发送，无需预知Content-Length</td>
          <td>动态内容传输</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>缓存控制</td>
          <td><code>Cache-Control</code>、<code>ETag</code>、<code>Last-Modified</code></td>
          <td>减少重复传输</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Host头</td>
          <td>支持同一IP多域名</td>
          <td>虚拟主机</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">HTTP/1.1 持久连接：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">客户端                  服务端
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  TCP握手                |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  | &lt;---------------------&gt; |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  GET /page1.html        |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  --------------------&gt;  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  200 OK                 |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  &lt;--------------------  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  GET /style.css         |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  --------------------&gt;  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  200 OK                 |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  &lt;--------------------  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  GET /image.jpg         |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  --------------------&gt;  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  200 OK                 |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  &lt;--------------------  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  Connection: close      |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  [可选挥手或保持]         |</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>HTTP/1.1 的队头阻塞问题</strong>：</p>]]></description></item><item><title>TCP vs UDP</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/tcp%E4%B8%8Eudp/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/tcp%E4%B8%8Eudp/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="tcp-vs-udp">TCP vs UDP</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：TCP通过三次握手、重传机制和流量控制实现可靠传输，适合数据完整性要求高的场景；UDP无连接、低延迟，适合实时性要求高于可靠性的场景。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="tcp通过连接管理和拥塞控制实现可靠传输udp以无连接和最小开销换取低延迟">TCP通过连接管理和拥塞控制实现可靠传输，UDP以无连接和最小开销换取低延迟</h2>
<h3 id="tcp核心机制可靠传输的三重保障">TCP核心机制：可靠传输的三重保障</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>机制</th>
          <th>解决的问题</th>
          <th>实现方式</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>连接管理</td>
          <td>端到端通信确认</td>
          <td>三次握手建立、四次挥手关闭</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>确认重传</td>
          <td>丢包恢复</td>
          <td>ACK确认 + 超时重传 + 快速重传</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>流量控制</td>
          <td>接收方处理不过来</td>
          <td>滑动窗口（rwnd）</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>拥塞控制</td>
          <td>网络拥塞</td>
          <td>慢启动、拥塞避免、快重传、快恢复</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>三次握手（建立连接）</strong>：</p>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">客户端                    服务端
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   |     SYN, seq=x      |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   | ------------------&gt; |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   |   SYN, ACK, seq=y, ack=x+1  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   | &lt;------------------ |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   |     ACK, seq=x+1, ack=y+1   |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   | ------------------&gt; |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   |                     |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ↓                     ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">ESTABLISHED           ESTABLISHED</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>为什么是三次？</strong></p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>